\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196570/extras/40c920838b46fb3cb8bd30811d94da49.poster.avif?t=1741891622\" width=610 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196570/extras/40c920838b46fb3cb8bd30811d94da49.webm?t=1741891622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196570/extras/40c920838b46fb3cb8bd30811d94da49.mp4?t=1741891622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Centered Around a Single Skill Release,</strong> but this skill can be linked with different support skill gems to achieve extraordinary effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skills Must Be Inserted into Equipment Slots.</strong> Support skills link to active skills, enhancing their effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Active Skills Determine the Type of Ability.</strong> Support gems only work when matched with a compatible active skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Equipment:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196570/extras/4503e90eed569a8721e459ad5219c0c6.poster.avif?t=1741891622\" width=610 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196570/extras/4503e90eed569a8721e459ad5219c0c6.webm?t=1741891622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196570/extras/4503e90eed569a8721e459ad5219c0c6.mp4?t=1741891622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>There are a lot of rare equipment with skill holes. The higher the rarity, the more guaranteed affixes. The same level of equipment has different combinations, and the random space is larger.</p>",
